						<div class="postbody">For backgrounds, yes. You also have attributes to worry about, they select which palette is used for each 16x16-pixel area of the screen, but you don't need to worry about creating this data manually if you use a program like NES Screen Tool. You can design your screens in it and export the data to be included in your ROM.</div>

